PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of State (Housing) of Jocelyne Bourgon, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a director of the Board of Directors of Canada Mortgage and Housing Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of three years, in the place of Dr. T. Russell Robinson, whose term has expired.
